  On a cache hit the value is read directly from ETS. On a miss `loader_fn` is
  called at most once, its result is cached, and `{:ok, value}` is returned.
  """
  @spec fetch(GenServer.server(), atom(), term(), (-> term())) :: {:ok, term()}
